im new to this board, im not really sure if the information is already posted somewhere on here or not, but if someone could help me that would be really cool. <br>
<br>
right now im a junior in high school. i want to go into video game design (im not sure what its really called) for college. i've planned on going to an art school since i can remember, but i also really like computers and using photoshop along with my art, plus i regularily play video games. this just seems like something that i'd really like to do.<br>
