<br>
Any art class you can get your hands on.<br>
Programming classes, specifically C/C++.<br>
Anatomy/Biology<br>
Philosophy<br>
3D visual mechanics classes<br>
Creative Writing<br>
Psychology<br>
Criminology (tags on to psych to help you learn how a baddy acts and thinks)<br>
Literature<br>
Tv production (if your school has it..mine has a tv/radio production thingy)<br>
Media Design<br>
<br>
Any ways these may not seem like very artsy classes, but when your trying to come up with a why a bad guy would possably want to destroy the world and just how that guy would look...it helps. The industry also wants well rounded people so that they can come up with an idea and/or deliver it with big flashing lights that do more than just look nice.<br>
<br>
You may also wanna look in the current or next issue of EGM they have a Designer wanna-be spot up in there...i dunno what month it is cuz i don't have it with me and i have a subscrition so i get them early...but it's the last one i recieved so it should either becoming to shelves soon or   jsut getting there. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=piggyinthemirror>PiggyInTheMirror</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Pre-Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(12/7/02 4:43:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4646.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re:</span><hr size=1> thank you for your help you guys! i've taken a few of the classes mention, but i have alot more to go. i'll check it out. thanks again.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=4646.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=4646.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4646.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.polykarbon.com/bbsimage/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=4646.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm2.threadControl?topicID=4646.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gi